<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Synnabot Status</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>Synnabot</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">A Powerful Discord Companion</p>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="status-box">
            <h2>Bot Status</h2>
            <span class="status-tag <%= status === 'online' ? 'online' : 'offline' %>">
                <%= status.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + status.slice(1) %>
            </span>
        </section>

        <section class="about">
            <h2>What is Synnabot?</h2>
            <p>Synnabot is a modern Discord bot built to empower your server with moderation tools, utilities, streamer integration, and smart AI assistance — all in one sleek package.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="features">
            <div class="feature">
            <h3>✨ Smart Commands</h3>
            <p>Custom commands like <code>!ask</code> powered by Gemini AI let users get instant answers.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
            <h3>🛡️ Role-Based Controls</h3>
            <p>Only trusted roles can run sensitive commands like setting birthdays or linking Twitch.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
            <h3>📅 Timezone & Birthday Tools</h3>
            <p>Track birthdays and show local time for users based on their timezone.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
            <h3>🎮 Twitch Integration</h3>
            <p>Keep your community updated with live streamer links and Twitch usernames.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="commands-preview">
            <h2>Quick Command Examples</h2>
            <div class="cmd-list">
            <code>!ping</code>
            <code>!add 5 10</code>
            <code>!setbirthday @User 29 03</code>
            <code>!ask What is AI?</code>
            </div>
            <a href="/docs" class="button">View Full Documentation</a>
        </section>

        <section class="buttons">
            <a href="/setup" class="button secondary">Set Up Locally</a>
        </section>  
        </main>


    <footer>
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Synnabot | Built by Azaken</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
